//! The model-driven tool loop: candidates → prompt contract → parse → validate
//! → metacog gate → MCP execute → feed the result back → loop until a plain
//! answer or the budget runs out.
//!
//! The prompt contract and 3-phase forgiving parser port the proven patterns
//! from apps/edge-workers/src/lib/tool-call-handler.ts (fenced ```tool_call
//! JSON, raw-JSON recovery, function-call-style recovery, hallucinated-name
//! rejection) onto small sovereign models.

